## ClientSDKHeaderValues.SEARCH\_CORE property

The SEARCH\_CORE agent should not be supplied. Instead, it will be automatically added to the header and populated with the version of Search Core being used.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
SEARCH_CORE?: never;
```
